    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1888-12-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1888-12-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="203" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d203">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Preston</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New
                                        York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-12-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 10,
                                    1888</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your note of Saturday just received. Being now empowered to sign protocol
                            for turning over the <hi rend="italic">Haytien Republic</hi> to the
                            United States, will send answer to note with draught protocol, and will
                            be Thursday at Department to sign protocol.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stephen Preston</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
